Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muginami! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan, you're so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you—!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Out of the way! Out of the way!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muginami!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just like kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mostly due to their craft's capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, standard fighter planes are no match for them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uehara!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell those three that they are not to fly into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing that Villagiulio hasn't made any moves lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we can't expect him to leave quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cap, you have an outside call.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tadokoro on Pharos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At what time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means he's practically here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calling all Vox Units.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Return to base immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to base?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? But the fun is just beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just get back here, stat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Tadokoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chairman will arrive at Pharos shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our boss, the Chairman of Novumundus!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chairman...?
