Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:29.39,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnPrototype\bord2\blur3\fad(850,750)\c&H393020&\pos(1049,111)\3c&H1E110A&}A Lolita in Kamogawa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Tadokoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are Syozo Tadokoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asteria Lizamarie De Roschefall...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be representing my great-grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Representing him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting older and doesn't like to travel long distances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we didn't receive a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a need?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there wasn't, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Tadokoro looks uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got more presence than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're the Vox pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was lying when I said that was a greeting on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Madoka Kyono?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so-so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'll make good scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have received detailed reports already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything that concerns you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been briefed quite thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to hear everything directly from the people who were involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Lan has met Asteria before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the one who taught Lan about the customs on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Woof" was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Woof" was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka Kyono.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me in your own words,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what happened during this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't remember very clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...well, we were having a little argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my temper and got upset with Muginami and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An argument?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tadokoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The report I received
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,said the cause was due to differences in tactical decisions made during an extreme battle situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, to be more precise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these girls were fighting amongst themselves during a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can explain,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that was a very important and sensitive problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of problem was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a girl like her would bring the legend to life?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Lan, let's get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Would you mind coming with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,It's not like you to want to make a stop somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to tell Madoka something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tend to be awkward about these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm concerned about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vox Legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I want
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a wider circuit laid between here and NORAD immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What are you crying about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You know you can be easily replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance, is the person on the other end of the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If you want to retain your position, listen to what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, Miss Nakaizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imaged Pharos having a room like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:08:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made them use lots of aged mahogany and oak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that being surrounded by steel and plastic corrupts a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is she really younger than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you to come here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to exchange information about Vox.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vox Legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard about it, Muginami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the scary story about Vox?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know that a story exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20,000 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,civilization on Earth once collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an archaeologist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what is your assessment of what the world was like 20,000 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would fall under the Last Glacial Maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there are no archaeological traces from that period.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So therefore you can't analyze it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too long ago, my answer would have been "yes."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20,000 years ago, a superior civilization existed on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the descendants of those who left Earth during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,So in a way, you and Muginami are both from this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Aren't you shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Sure, I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,But also a little disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,if you're both earthlings, this is like coming home for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Huh? Coming home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They're so talented!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,our ancestors left this planet 20,000 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,after a great war took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,It was because the Vox had lost control,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,nearly destroying the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant green demon will sunder the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant blue demon will devour the stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant orange demon will spew out darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through countless sacrifices, they will rule the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeding off a tainted heart, they awaken from within the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the demons shall rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This poem has been passed down for generations in Le Garite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My older brother used to scare me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by saying a giant blue demon was going to eat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant blue demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that something like the boogeyman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New nations were established in a faraway galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a pact was signed to preserve Earth, where man originated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We established Earth as an inviolable neutral territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and severed all contact with those who remained.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We feared that the Circle of Rin-ne forged by the Vox
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would once again destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what happened, then why did two come to this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has changed and the Vox has become necessary again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this has served to revive the legend as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an archeologist and have researched the Vox for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like you to shed some new light on this legend, from your vantage point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a fan of science fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me put it this way then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child who ran away
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because of familial strife, returns now only to claim his inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if you were the parent?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd give him a good punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant blue demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, are you still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sleep here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet you're the one who's actually scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered the scary story from this afternoon and got frightened didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! A demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, little Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be afraid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midori isn't a demon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I touched Midori,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had this nostalgic feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've known Midori from long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that meeting Midori was fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so poetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's illogical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And demons are logical?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we turn in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the legend is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, the Earth really may be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prevent the tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that occurred 20,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of this moment, all operations associated with Vox Aura will be shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am banning Madoka Kyono from piloting Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I might cause Midori to lose control again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please rescind your orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You based your decision on a groundless legend that's never been proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with Lan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with piloting Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know the legend surrounding the Vox,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continuing to operate Aura poses a risk that cannot be ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg your pardon,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't believe we can put up any resistance without Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Request denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set up a defense strategy immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,centered on Vox Lympha and Ignis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the decision reached by the Novumundus High Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will not be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things won't go "perfect" this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do, Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cap, it's Kyono.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Tadokoro, what's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laffinty and Muginami are responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've locked themselves up in there and won't open the door
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until we rescind the orders to shut down Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are those two doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you put them up to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, those two are going the extra mile for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muginami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is all this nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just like children whose toys were confiscated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All entries have been locked from the inside and we can't access them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go in and talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let this go on, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you intend to get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed that you thought of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the parent's job to spank children who don't listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you go along with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was quite sure that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if anyone tried to do something, it would be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in too much pain to think of an answer.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.37,0:17:05.67,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\blur0.65\bord0\c&H311A19&\frz359.155\pos(854,346)}We Oppose The \NShutdown Of \N{\fs40\c&H96AE3A&}Aura{sign}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:05.67,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(0,0)\bord0\blur0.5\p1\c&HEEF1F0&}m 755 235 l 755 353 l 954 358 l 954 236 {p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Lan... Muginami...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite an unusual experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we ask you to reconsider?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka and Aura are both essential to our team.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be uneasy if it's just Lan and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate what you're doing, but this isn't the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that means we won't be able to fly together anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be terrible if what happened last time repeats itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it does, I'll stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it doesn't stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it doesn't stop, I'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Madoka of the Sweats Club would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thought of you two getting hurt because of me is even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the confidence to promise that it won't lose control again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just not that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, even if I can't pilot Midori,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not like you and Lan are going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Ms. Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the answer to my earlier question?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only ordered Aura to be grounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't pilot Midori,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing will change between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will always be the Kamo Girls' Sweats Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I feel so stupid for doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Disregard it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you'll overlook everything regarding this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a serious violation of service regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my decision as the representative of the Novumundus High Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how are the preparations to equip Lympha and Ignis proceeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Equip"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out immediately and get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the ship ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must be even more wary of the actions of those who oppose
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the blossoming of the Circle of Rin-ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, since Villagiulio is openly taking action,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we cannot waste any time whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then speed up the retrieval schedule for the Vox units as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't it ironic, Moid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The light moves so slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but time cruelly pushes us forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Array...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the—!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, just don't look, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the personal maid for the Chairman of Novumundus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what is your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not hand over the Vox to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll live to regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flower of Lagrange
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must never be allowed to blossom again.
